#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><ul><li>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:367
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    <uri link=\"#ifconfig_route\">Using ifconfig and route</uri> explains how to\n"
"    set up your networking manually\n"
"  "
msgstr ""
"    <uri link=\"#ifconfig_route\">ifconfigとrouteの設定</uri>は、ネットワークを手動で設定する方法の説明です。\n"
