msgid "Using ifconfig and route"
msgstr "ifconfigとrouteの設定"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:615
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Setting up your network consists of three steps. First we assign\n"
"ourselves an IP address using <c>ifconfig</c>. Then we set up routing to\n"
"the gateway using <c>route</c>. Then we finish up by placing the\n"
"nameserver IPs in <path>/etc/resolv.conf</path>.\n"
msgstr ""
"ネットワークの設定は3段階から成ります。\n"
"最初に、<c>ifconfig</c>を使用して自分自身のIPアドレスを割当てます。\n"
"次に、<c>route</c>を使用しゲートウェイへのルーティングを設定します。\n"
"そして最後に、<path>/etc/resolv.conf</path>にネームサーバーのIPアドレスを記述します。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:622
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To assign an IP address, you will need your IP address, broadcast\n"
"address and netmask. Then execute the following command, substituting\n"
"<c>${IP_ADDR}</c> with your IP address, <c>${BROADCAST}</c> with your\n"
"broadcast address and <c>${NETMASK}</c> with your netmask:\n"
msgstr ""
"IPアドレスを設定するために、IPアドレス、ブロードキャストアドレス、\n"
"ネットマスクが必要です。\n"
"そして、<c>${IP_ADDR}</c>をIPアドレスに、\n"
"<c>${BROADCAST}</c>をブロードキャストアドレスに、\n"
"<c>${NETMASK}</c>をネットマスクに置換して、次のコマンドを実行します。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:628
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using ifconfig"
msgstr "ifconfigの使用"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:629
#, no-wrap
msgid "# <i>ifconfig eth0 ${IP_ADDR} broadcast ${BROADCAST} netmask ${NETMASK} up</i>\n"
msgstr "# <i>ifconfig eth0 ${IP_ADDR} broadcast ${BROADCAST} netmask ${NETMASK} up</i>\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:633
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Now set up routing using <c>route</c>. Substitute <c>${GATEWAY}</c> with\n"
"your gateway IP address:\n"
msgstr ""
"さて、<c>route</c>を使用してルーティングの設定です。\n"
"<c>${GATEWAY}</c>をゲートウェイアドレスに置換します。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:637
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using route"
msgstr "routeの使用"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:638
#, no-wrap
msgid "# <i>route add default gw ${GATEWAY}</i>\n"
msgstr "# <i>route add default gw ${GATEWAY}</i>\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:642
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Now open <path>/etc/resolv.conf</path> with your favorite editor (in our\n"
"example, we use <c>nano</c>):\n"
msgstr ""
"そして、好きなエディタで(この例ではnanoを使います)\n"
"<path>/etc/resolv.conf</path>を開きます。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:646
#, no-wrap
msgid "Creating /etc/resolv.conf"
msgstr "/etc/resolv.confの作成"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:647
#, no-wrap
msgid "# <i>nano -w /etc/resolv.conf</i>\n"
msgstr "# <i>nano -w /etc/resolv.conf</i>\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:651
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Now fill in your nameserver(s) using the following as a template. Make\n"
"sure you substitute <c>${NAMESERVER1}</c> and <c>${NAMESERVER2}</c> with\n"
"the appropriate nameserver addresses:\n"
msgstr ""
"次のテンプレートを使ってネームサーバーを記述します。\n"
"<c>${NAMESERVER1}</c>と<c>${NAMESERVER2}</c>を適切なネームサーバーアドレスに置換するのを忘れないでください。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:656
#, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/resolv.conf template"
msgstr "/etc/resolv.confテンプレート"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:657
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"nameserver ${NAMESERVER1}\n"
"nameserver ${NAMESERVER2}\n"
msgstr ""
"nameserver ${NAMESERVER1}\n"
"nameserver ${NAMESERVER2}\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-network.xml:662
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"That's it. Now test your network by pinging some Internet server (like\n"
"<uri link=\"http://www.google.com\">Google</uri>). If this works,\n"
"congratulations then. You are now ready to install Gentoo. Continue with <uri\n"
"link=\"?part=1&amp;chap=4\">Preparing the Disks</uri>.\n"
msgstr ""
"これですべてです。\n"
"インターネットサーバーのホスト(例えば<uri link=\"http://www.google.com\">Google</uri>)へpingをして、ネットワークのテストをしてください。\n"
"もしそれがうまくいったら、おめでとう。\n"
"Gentooをインストールする準備ができました。\n"
"<uri\n"
"link=\"?part=1&amp;chap=4\">ディスクの準備</uri>へ進んでください。\n"
